30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aebbe564d9f7bfaa4cbc3d9f86241751b91dd89a","tid":477840,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"大葉黎 食得"},{"pid":"b71db73e9b169bcd23d0711f51ecba50b8a978bc","tid":477840,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"炸得畀你緊係食得"},{"pid":"45392b205d9e3af54d4ae0d6edece7ae96ca3278","tid":477840,"uid":21678,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先食飯嗌左個天婦羅 <br />\n<br />\n想問塊葉炸得咁靚係咪預俾我食? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bsho30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fbsho30.jpg&h=2ce63066&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢塊紫蘇葉嚟<br />\n（即係用嚟蒸大閘蟹果塊）<br />\n<br />\n中醫角度呢塊嘢可以驅寒，大肚婆都要食佢<br />\n而蟹、海鮮都係性寒涼<br />\n所以要食呢塊嘢中和番<br />\n你啲天婦羅以海鮮為主，梗係要食番塊落去頂住<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n超級巿場果啲盒裝壽司中間果塊膠葉<br />\n其實都係扮緊呢塊嘢"},{"pid":"c25ebd75c9c555ed9a5a8fdcf21b6e68fb15e5b7","tid":477840,"uid":30927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先食飯嗌左個天婦羅 <br />\n<br />\n想問塊葉炸得咁靚係咪預俾我食? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bsho30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fbsho30.jpg&h=2ce63066&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢塊紫蘇葉嚟<br />\n（即係用嚟蒸大閘蟹果塊）<br />\n<br />\n中醫角度呢塊嘢可以驅寒，大肚婆都要食佢<br />\n而蟹、海鮮都係性寒涼<br />\n所以要食呢塊嘢中和番<br />\n你啲天婦羅以海鮮為主，梗係要食番塊落去頂住<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n超級巿場果啲盒裝壽司中間果塊膠葉<br />\n其實都係扮緊呢塊嘢</blockquote><br />\n長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fd757193f005496e738fd50dd584850bcd7b80","tid":477840,"uid":79469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"唔食得嫁 多數係拎黎比你妹下妹下"}]}